	Small cleanups.
	Use GstSegment.
	Add simple frame dropping QoS.
	Precalc buffer output sizes and UV offsets.
	Always give libmpeg2 a valid fbuf when it wants one.
	don't trust libmpeg to discard our buffers but manage it
	ourselves.
	Fixes #343627, #335288

