	(gst_mad_check_caps_reset), (gst_mad_chain):
	  Merge patch from Radoslaw Szkodzinski (bug 326734)

2006-01-31  Stefan Kost  <ensonic@users.sf.net>

	* ext/mad/gstid3tag.c: (tag_list_to_id3_tag_foreach),
